name: AutoCreep
tagline: Automatically creep on friends who use Twitter
body:
#Autocreep ![Logo](http://i.imgur.com/E0RrYYr.png)
This project is for automating the creep process. It downloads the most recent 200 tweets and filters through them to find common words, therefore automating the creep process.
This is a CodeDay 2015 Minneapolis Entry
